Narrative: 
On May 16, 2023, I, Corporal Nicholas R. Hager, #6001, of the Maryland State Police Criminal Enforcement Division Eastern Region received CyberTipline Report 160159282 from the National Center for Missing and Exploited Children. In CyberTipline Report 160159282 Google reported that a subject uploaded child pornography to the internet on 04-09-2023 at 15:55:40 UTC. I reviewed the reported media and confirmed that it does in-fact depict child pornography and can be described as the following:

Filename: cqHSeg_Lh2w.mp4
Description: One video thirteen (13) seconds in length depicting an animated scene with the label 2013 at the bottom. Within the animated scene is a television which is playing a video depicting a human prepubescent male under the age of sixteen (16) (approximately 3 to 5 years of age). The male can be observed fully nude, seated with his legs spread and his penis exposed. The male can be observed turning to the side with his right hand on his buttocks. The animation then changes to what appears to be a movie theater with the label 2023. The movie theater screen depicts a human prepubescent male under the age of sixteen (16) (approximately 3 to 5 years of age) exposing his anus to the camera. 
  
Google provided the following information in reference to the suspect:

Name: Monique Paul
Mobile Phone: +14438596034 (Verified 07-10-2021 03:38:33 UTC)
Mobile Phone: +15614025733 (Verified 11-02-2022 02:20:13 UTC)
Date of Birth: 06-07-1976
Email Address: pmonique308@gmail.com (Verified)
IP Address: 2601:153:880:92a0:6153:eaaf:8196:722f (Login) 04-10-2023 03:22:00 UTC
IP Address: 2601:153:880:92a0:6153:eaaf:8196:722f (Login) 04-09-2023 03:15:20 UTC

Google also provided the following URL in reference to the uploaded video:
http://youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3DcqHSeg_Lh2w

I conducted an open source search of phone number +14438596034 which revealed that it is registered to T-Mobile. I also conducted a search of the above listed IP Address which revealed that it was registered to Comcast Cable Communications. The above listed phone number and IP Address geo-locate to the Salisbury, Wicomico County, Maryland Area.

Case open, investigation continuing.

Narrative: 
On September 13, 2023, I, Corporal Nicholas R. Hager, #6001 of the Maryland State Police Criminal Enforcement Division Eastern Region made contact with Monique Paul [hereinafter referred to as Monique] at 1710 Emerson Avenue, Salisbury, Wicomico County, Maryland. While contacting Monique, it was learned that she is not fluent in the English Language. I communicated with Monique utilizing a Haitian Creole interpreter from Language Line Solutions #419333. While speaking with Monique, I learned that she has three children who reside at the residence. Monique said her children are 16 years of age, 7 years of age, and 4 years of age. Monique identified her 4-year-old who matches the description from the reported video of approximately 3 to 5 years of age as Wendersky Villanoix. Monique said she has a YouTube account and identified the above listed account as hers. Monique also said that her son Wendersky often accesses YouTube utilizing her account.

An internet safety talk was conducted with Monique during which the laws pertaining to child pornography and concepts of monitoring what her children are doing on the internet to promote a safe and healthy internet experience for her children were relayed to her.
